description.plain: Tai Verdes, formerly tylersemicolon, is a 24-year-old singer/songwriter from Los Angeles, California. He has a versatile style, showing influences of R&B, rap and pop. He has performed on various platforms, with his biggest break on MTV. He began his career with his long time friend, Ethan “Emoney” Cohen, creating buzz with several singles, then moved to solo work.
